name: my destiny - #Floripa 1
description:
my destiny - Floripa #1

This was taken in 2012 in Florianópolis, Brazil. My home town.

my destiny is the genesis collection of brazilian photographer RUA. 

A collection of frames taken between 2011 and 2020 while wandering through Brazil and Latin America. Each trip made possible by a mixture of fortunate situations, being there was destiny. These are the feelings of each place.
